snippet: The Chargers’ Seyi Ajirotutu was fined $27,562 for making contact with an official, and four Ravens were fined a total of $44,804.
abstract: NFL Roundup; San Diego Chargers receiver Seyi Ajirotutu is fined $27,562 by the NFL for making contact with an official during loss to the Miami Dolphins; other football news noted.
lead_paragraph: The Chargers’ Seyi Ajirotutu was fined $27,562 for making contact with an official, and four Ravens were fined a total of $44,804.
